00:50.614 --> 00:51.215
Amen?

00:51.235 --> 00:52.257
So, glory to God.

00:52.838 --> 00:55.442
So we're talking about, really,

00:55.554 --> 01:05.286
embracing the kingdom of God and what makes the kingdom of God work and what makes the kingdom of darkness thrive.

01:05.346 --> 01:15.198
And what we want to do is we want to be strong in what makes the kingdom of light work and then shun away from what makes the kingdom of darkness work.

01:15.919 --> 01:24.850
And sometimes as Christians, we can walk in the dark at times, but we don't need to, we don't have to, and you can walk in the light, amen?

01:25.154 --> 01:28.679
And so I love this in Matthew 633, amplified.

01:29.260 --> 01:46.066
