02:18.324 --> 02:19.906
Order starts coming in.

02:20.547 --> 02:22.309
Peace starts coming in.

02:22.369 --> 02:23.570
The grace

02:23.682 --> 02:25.605
starts coming in, glory to God.

02:26.226 --> 02:26.867
