03:10.820 --> 03:11.461
Amen.

03:12.222 --> 03:12.542
Amen.

03:12.603 --> 03:14.986
But we're in a, somebody say, I'm in a process.

03:16.348 --> 03:17.490
I'm getting better.

03:18.466 --> 03:19.347
Amen.

03:19.607 --> 03:22.730
