03:38.104 --> 03:41.508
So we see that pride will cause you to fall.

03:42.028 --> 03:45.612
Humility will God will raise you up.

03:45.672 --> 03:48.274
In other words, God's looking to promote some of us.

03:49.314 --> 03:55.302
So I'm gonna say this, the more humble you become, the more usable you become of God.

03:56.584 --> 03:59.408
The more humble you are, the more God can use you.

03:59.448 --> 04:06.017
The less humble you are, the more pride for you are, the less God can use you or promote you or bless you.

04:06.958 --> 04:11.785
And so the second week, we talked about greed versus generosity.

04:11.825 --> 04:16.191
