04:16.912 --> 04:18.194
Have you noticed that?

04:18.882 --> 04:32.455
and the human nature is very selfish and we can be tempted with a spirit of selfishness at times in our walk and sometimes greed will try to work in a believer's life, amen?

04:33.096 --> 04:40.383
And so we talked about this last week that really you need to overcome greed by being generous.

04:40.944 --> 04:43.166
Somebody say I'm a generous person.

04:44.587 --> 04:47.410
Now I know some of you have to say that by faith, amen?

04:47.682 --> 04:50.526
But we are generous people, amen?

04:50.987 --> 04:54.592
And it's God's love that causes us to be generous.

04:54.672 --> 05:01.262
Last week I talked about one of the keys to killing greed or selfishness out of our life.

05:02.023 --> 05:04.647
