05:05.268 --> 05:09.575
Now I didn't focus too much on the tithe, I just kind of hit on it just a little bit.

05:10.235 --> 05:14.642
But the tithe means that you're giving God, now brace yourself,

05:15.074 --> 05:19.999
Buckle up means that you're giving God 10% of your income.

05:20.059 --> 05:20.560
What?

05:21.661 --> 05:25.545
That means if you make $100 a week, you give God $10.

05:25.605 --> 05:28.848
