05:28.868 --> 05:29.529
$10.

05:30.070 --> 05:33.533
That means if you make $1,000 a week, you give God $100.

05:34.855 --> 05:38.078
That means if you make $10,000 a week, you give God $1,000.

05:39.820 --> 05:41.842
I think you're getting the better end of the deal.

05:42.786 --> 05:47.531
That means God is saying, you can keep 90%, but I just want you to give me 10%.

05:48.212 --> 05:52.877
And I'm telling you this, that God is looking to bless us.

05:53.558 --> 05:55.640
God is looking to bless your life, amen?

05:56.180 --> 05:58.703
And so he wants you to give your first and your best.

05:58.783 --> 06:03.448
In Malachi, it says in Malachi 3, he says, well, a man robbed God.

06:04.509 --> 06:06.832
