06:07.152 --> 06:08.834
Malachi is prophesied to the people.

06:08.854 --> 06:12.658
He says, you have robbed me, but you say, in what way have we robbed you?

06:12.802 --> 06:15.204
they weren't even aware that they were robbing God.

06:15.685 --> 06:18.548
And they said, in ties and offerings.

06:19.088 --> 06:21.931
So this is the thing that I like to interpret this way.

06:22.552 --> 06:27.797
We rob God of his ability when we don't tithe to bless us.

06:28.437 --> 06:31.740
