13:30.676 --> 13:35.122
Now today I want to focus on fear versus faith.

13:35.618 --> 13:39.804
The devil's number one weapon against the believer is fear.

13:40.645 --> 13:45.492
Acronym of fear is fear is false evidence appearing real.

13:46.113 --> 13:46.433
Amen?

13:47.134 --> 13:49.918
I like what Paul said to Timothy.

13:50.299 --> 13:58.150
He said that God has not given us a spirit of fear, but a power, love, and a sound mind.

13:58.170 --> 14:04.018
Now if you want to take the word fear and break it down to another level, you could say worry.

14:04.450 --> 14:07.034
Because most people say, I'm not in fear, but are you worrying?

14:08.156 --> 14:10.079
But if you're worrying, you're in fear.

14:10.639 --> 14:11.000
Amen?

14:11.461 --> 14:13.864
And the Lord doesn't want us to worry.

14:14.065 --> 14:14.425
Amen?

14:14.846 --> 14:17.109
Pray about everything and fear nothing.

14:18.151 --> 14:18.371
Amen.

14:18.391 --> 14:18.552
Amen.

14:18.992 --> 14:22.117
So you pray about everything and you fear nothing.

14:22.538 --> 14:25.302
So the devil's never one weapon against a believer is fear.

14:25.823 --> 14:33.234
The devil uses fear against us to keep us from doing the will of God in our lives or to corrupt the will of God in our lives.

14:33.666 --> 14:38.071
So the devil will try to keep you from doing what God wants you to do.

14:38.111 --> 14:40.934
And what God wants you to do is not bad.

14:40.994 --> 14:50.965
Sometimes God wants you to maybe start a business, maybe do something different, maybe go witness to your neighbor, whatever the Lord wants you to do.

14:50.985 --> 14:56.852
And a lot of times it's fear that's keeping us back from doing what God wants us to do.

14:56.892 --> 14:58.694
Is that right?

14:59.495 --> 15:02.578
One of the greatest fears that the devil

15:02.850 --> 15:05.614
