17:20.456 --> 17:24.862
God thinks highly of people that put their trust in God.

17:25.263 --> 17:26.184
Do you believe that today?

17:26.244 --> 17:27.025
Amen.

17:27.406 --> 17:34.797
So my question to you today, are you putting your trust in people or are you putting your trust in God?

17:35.578 --> 17:38.682
And I'm gonna say this, I'm gonna put my trust in God.

17:38.722 --> 17:46.834
Now, I'm not saying don't trust people because you're gonna, you have to work with people, you're gonna have to deal with people, you're gonna have to give them a measure of trust.

17:47.362 --> 17:49.665
but don't give them ultimate trust.

17:50.345 --> 17:57.493
In other words, don't think that they're gonna be like Jesus and never make a mistake because people will make mistakes, amen?

17:58.134 --> 18:14.693
So the Lord, so I like this because we gotta put our trust in God and I like what it says in Psalms 118 verse six, working our way down, it says, the Lord is for me so I will have no fear what can mere people do to me.

18:15.013 --> 18:15.634
I love that.

18:16.162 --> 18:18.525
